Change log of sxg's ksocket project

2008-05-15, ksocket version 0.0.2
  o add KSOCKET_ADDR_SAFE macro for speed consideration
  o add tcp client sample code
  o other minor changes

2007-09-09, ksocket version 0.0.1
  o original version of ksocket
  o provides the following BSD-style socket interfaces
    *ksocket, kshutdown, kclose
    *kbind, klisten, kconnect, kaccept
    *krecv, ksend, krecvfrom, ksendto
    *kgetsockname, kgetpeername, ksetsockopt

